      "text": [
        "4658 - قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: \"أَوَّلُ اَلنَّظْرَةِ لَكَ وَ اَلثَّانِيَةُ عَلَيْكَ وَ لاَ لَكَ وَ اَلثَّالِثَةُ فِيهَا اَلْهَلاَكُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4658 - Imam (as) said: \"The first glance is for you, the second is against you and not for you, and the third in it is destruction.\""
        ]
      }
    }
